ri_Huske\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\"}, {\"begin\": 3521, \"end\": 3528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9972926071727616, \"rank\": 0.002714742689975867, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the semi-finals of the women's 50m freestyle, Sweden's Sarah Sjoestroem set a new Olympic record with her swim of 23.66, the third-fastest time in history.\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3599, \"end\": 3605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9905674331235172, \"rank\": 0.008545650835554967, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3608, \"end\": 3613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\", \"score\": 0.6762139649199713, \"rank\": 0.3917126690911472, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Additional input from AFP  Copyright \\u00a9 2025.\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The News International, All Rights Reserved\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3761, \"end\": 3783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The News International\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\"}]}]}"